-- 01_customer_channel_attribution.sql
```sql
WITH latest_attribution AS (
  SELECT
    customer_id,
    channel,
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY customer_id ORDER BY attributed_at DESC) as rn
  FROM customer_channels
)
SELECT
  customer_id,
  channel
FROM latest_attribution
WHERE rn = 1
```

-- 02_customer_revenue_by_channel.sql
```sql
SELECT
  COALESCE(ca.channel, 'unattributed') as channel,
  COALESCE(s.city, 'unknown') as city,
  SUM(t.amount) as total_revenue,
  COUNT(t.transaction_id) as transaction_count,
  COUNT(DISTINCT t.customer_id) as unique_customers
FROM transactions t
LEFT JOIN (
  WITH latest_attribution AS (
    SELECT
      customer_id,
      channel,
      ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY customer_id ORDER BY attributed_at DESC) as rn
    FROM customer_channels
  )
  SELECT customer_id, channel
  FROM latest_attribution
  WHERE rn = 1
) ca ON t.customer_id = ca.customer_id
LEFT JOIN stores s ON t.store_id = s.store_id
GROUP BY COALESCE(ca.channel, 'unattributed'), COALESCE(s.city, 'unknown')
ORDER BY total_revenue DESC
